data.description: Price improved to SELL. Conveniently located close to the highway, parks & shopping but nestled in a luxurious neighborhood for a quiet oasis. Upon approaching the front door, this 2383 sf home offers an inviting foyer, a large kitchen with granite countertops, in-sink island, great room, formal dining & living areas, large primary with outdoor access, separated bedrooms from the primary hall for extra privacy. This floor plan offers enough room to entertain many family & friends but also offers a low maintenance yard. Come take a tour and start your new year with a new home.
